<HEADLINE>
FT  30 JUN 94 / Postal plans
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The government's green paper on the future of the Post Office is to be
published today. The three main options are: a 51 per cent sale of the Royal
Mail and Parcelforce; a 49 per cent sale of the two companies; and more
commercialisation in the public sector.
